Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:44.11,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Like sunshine trickling through the leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:48.07,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I want to feel something real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:51.55,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Like rivers overflowing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:55.83,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I want to be set free
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:59.45,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Now everything is polythene
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:03.68,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}A world in which nothing's real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:07.19,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I don't know where we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:11.11,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Now won't you come find me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.06,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Though I try, and I try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:15.02,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}And I try, and I try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.69,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Can never shake off this feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:20.93,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Don't know why, don't know why
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.91,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Don't know why, don't know why
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:26.78,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Why we hide from you
