Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:35.09,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Something's pulling me, I move ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.99,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Threads
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:47.60,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}What is holding is also being held
