Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:08.13,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}我們再也不會見到它們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.39,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}我找到了一條被遺忘的小徑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.40,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}那裡已經雜草叢生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.59,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}循著自己的足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:21.75,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}我一個人向著那裡走去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:28.31,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:35.09,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}它拽著我向前進
